&lt;li&gt;Mentor engineers in profiling, tuning, and low-level optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with hardware vendors and infra teams to maximize cluster utilization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
